


<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="quote quote--big quote--navy">
    <span>Our Adventure Begins</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="schedule">
    <span class="schedule__title">On the Day</span>
    <div class="schedule__container">
        <p class="schedule__subTitle">The Wedding - 4:30 PM</p>
        <p class="schedule__text">The wedding will be held at the Hyatt in Sarasota, FL.</p>
        <p class="schedule__subTitle">Cocktail Hour - 5 PM</p>
        <p class="schedule__text">The Cocktail Hour will commence at the end of the ceremony.  It will be located next to the Tiki Bar by the pool, adjacent to the ceremony location.</p>
        <p class="schedule__subTitle">The Reception - 6 PM</p>
        <p class="schedule__text">Dinner, drinks, and dancing to follow at the Boat House.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info">
    <span class="info__title">About Us</span>
    <div class="info__container">
        <p class="info__subTitle">How They Met</p>
        <p class="info__text">Kristin and Corey met on a bike ride on New Years Eve in 2013.  Together, they enjoy long distance triathlon, travelling, and hanging out with their two dogs, Rory and Logan.</p>
        <p class="info__text">Corey proposed to Kristin after a bike ride on New Year's Eve at Lido Beach, one of their favorite places.</p>
        <p class="info__text">They are always up for a new adventure.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="info info--top">
        <span class="info__title">Accomodations</span>
        <div class="info__container">
            <p class="info__subTitle">Hyatt Regency Sarasota</p>
            <p class="info__text info__text--black"><a href="https://resweb.passkey.com/go/LyonsMcClellandWedding">Register</a> at the Hyatt.  The Hyatt is the wedding venue.  A block of rooms is available.</p>
            <p class="info__subTitle">Hotel Indigo Sarasota</p>
            <p class="info__text info__text--black"><a href="http://www.srqhotel.com/">Register</a> Modern hotel across from the Hyatt.</p>
            <p class="info__subTitle">Lido Beach Resort</p>
            <p class="info__text info__text--black"><a href="http://www.lidobeachresort.com/">Register</a> Resort hotel that's right on the beach.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info info--top">
        <span class="info__title">Points of Interest</span>
        <div class="info__container">
            <p class="info__subTitle">Lido Beach</p>
            <p class="info__text">Located on Lido Key, one half mile southwest of St. Armand's Circle, this beach has it all! More than 3,000 feet of pristine white sand, concession and gift shop, restrooms, picnic tables and a pool.</p>
            <p class="info__subTitle">Ringling Museum</p>
            <p class="info__text">The John and Mable Ringling Museum of Art is the state art museum of Florida, located in Sarasota, Florida. It was established in 1927 as the legacy of Mable and John Ringling for the people of Florida.</p>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>

